Model install and initialization
========================================================
- Install using `devtools` or `remotes`
- Requires a C++ compiler and `Rcpp`
```{r}
require(Rcpp)
#remotes::install_github("nmfs-fish-tools/RMAS")
devtools::load_all(".")

r4mas <-
  Module("rmas", dyn.load(paste("src/RMAS", .Platform$dynlib.ext, sep = "")))
```

